 The Nigerian National Petroleum Corporation, NNPC, yesterday, said it has secured a $1.16 million grant from the United States Trade and Development Agency, USTDA, being part funding for the 1,350 megawatts, MW, electricity NNPC-Abuja Independent Power Project, IPP. Continue reading NNPC secures $1.16m grant from USTDA for 1,350mw power plant at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard